# Heap Generations

Heap Memory is divided into different generations.

```text
Heap
│
├── Young Generation
│     ├── Eden Space
│     ├── Survivor S0
│     └── Survivor S1
│
└── Old (Tenured) Generation
```

## Young Generation

- New objects are created here.
- Minor Garbage Collection occurs here.

## Old Generation

- Objects that survive multiple Minor GCs are promoted here.
- Major Garbage Collection occurs here.

